| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2394 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 586e2c74-e45a-5c6a-b4b2-b1a190a9b900"
